{"tid":2053962,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[慶祝Korean Fish落台系列] 極權說話方式入門:doublethink","createTime":"2020-06-06T17:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T02:14:28.000Z","uid":50884,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07884ad7915d94ff24e00cbcbf4590c63185d252","tid":2053962,"uid":50884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:54:31.000Z","msg":"今日社交媒體有好多罷韓告捷的消息，當然可喜可賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但令人感興趣嘅是，韓總面對如此難堪嘅局面，仍不忘消費果一百三十萬冇投票嘅高雄人，作為他面書置頂信息的延續<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NkwaDu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NkwaDu.png&h=6fcd6d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPs:已經好心幫大家blur左佢個樣<br />\n<br />\n當大家笑鳩他「落地拿渣沙」、「沉默大多數」之時，又有冇諗過依個舉動係一粒繼續餵俾佢啲韓粉嘅藍色藥丸？甚至背後隱藏住極權國家嘅意識形態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLhZjx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLhZjx4.jpg&h=274ce0a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上約一百字的信息，呼籲支持者<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>係琴日（6/6）投票，並褒揚 「不投票的行為」為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">表達自己意見</span></span>的方式、而且既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不激化</span></span>又<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不對立</span></span>更是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不政治化嘅處理手段</span></span>。聰明的您，應該看出端倪了，投票，唔係就係民主社會一個主要表達意見嘅途徑咩？依種認知上嘅矛盾，被George Orwell定義為 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Doublethink(雙重思想)</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQuoted from wiki:<br />\n<blockquote>知與不知，知道全部真實情況而卻扯些滴水不漏的謊話，同時持兩種互相抵消的觀點，明知它們互相矛盾而仍都相信，用邏輯來反邏輯，一邊表示擁護道德一邊又否定道德，一邊相信民主是辦不到的一邊又相信黨是民主的捍衛者，忘掉一切必須忘掉的東西而又在需要的時候想起它來，然後又馬上忘掉它，而尤其是，把這樣的做法應用到做法本身上面&mdash;&mdash;這可謂絕妙透頂了：有意識地進入無意識，而後又並不意識到你剛才完成的催眠。即使要了解&ldquo;雙重思想&rdquo;的含義你也得使用雙重思想。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&lt;1984&gt;裡的三句: War Is Peace; Freedom Is Slavery; Ignorance Is Strength 就當然係doublethink的應用。係小說入面，單一執政嘅Ingsoc(英社)擁護寡頭政治，但同時又自詡為民主的守護者。係現實中，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有個係WTO就永遠話自己發展中國家，係國際社會就也文也武嘅天朝大國成撚日都讚自己係最有特色嘅民主國家</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而香港嘅doublethink代表，當然唔少得我地天才般嘅容海恩議員<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vKztcYT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvKztcYT.jpg&h=a89c9fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(議會必然係講政治嘅地方)<br />\n<br />\n同777<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OWwrJ6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOWwrJ6a.png&h=7599c3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(香港高度自治...ar ha?)<br />\n<br />\n返返我地韓總嘅case，就睇得出韓總，或者佢背後嘅人對罷韓公投嘅呼籲，一早就超越<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投與不投</span></span>嘅二元問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而更似係一個反民主制度嘅思想植入</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於背後咩人想輸出依種意識形態？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kfb7tDa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkfb7tDa.png&h=e0757645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結語:</span></ins><br />\nDoublethink唔單只係一種語言藝術咁簡單，背後仲可以配合其他邏輯謬誤，做到思想控制嘅效果(有人想睇再寫)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟第一次係學術台開po<br />\n求下大家睇完留個名又好，有錯請插<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5dfe371a55355b4ff9c7656e08bc5aa57ed12b","tid":2053962,"uid":50884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:56:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"bb11ddcced1062a75631e2a2c541d9892cb86dcb","tid":2053962,"uid":50884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"478672a031c37f12c72407c0449a7c104232cb8a","tid":2053962,"uid":50884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2569a1aac1b8e2371654b4673b4ee327facf690","tid":2053962,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836b2dde8bcf87bbb1fa6d08ac3a8d7229089012","tid":2053962,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.g