a157a489bb10457188578604dae8e34642a56","tid":2053962,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7204c0c09f89f5e7fb4a6f0f6f58d1302cf9dc76","tid":2053962,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b611cd47d8eec607666f99d13137557ed1ba97","tid":2053962,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T18:04:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c8b85d08a1f6dd0d78dc0bb0346654b525d6503","tid":2053962,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T18:11:08.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1dd2d9aee044a3a16430cb41b11e00422c882523","tid":2053962,"uid":17039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T18:18:19.000Z","msg":"留名等學嘢"},{"pid":"dcde2342b7f1a9b16fe9930fd7b4115e7ade7952","tid":2053962,"uid":131600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T18:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316814a5d1c0a745819c44022b2adf628c38dc33","tid":2053962,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T00:26:05.000Z","msg":"的確冇講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以唔好再話佢地蠢/fake news on9冇人睇<br />\n真蠢只會做一次，做得多一定有佢既理由<br />\n<br />\n策略上，循例點都要餵返啲blue pill俾支持者食<br />\n因為佢地最怕既係啲人食red pill"},{"pid":"f8eb414ef3a674b70f79391228d06ca93e3afaca","tid":2053962,"uid":50884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"316814a5d1c0a745819c44022b2adf628c38dc33","tid":2053962,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T00:26:05.000Z","msg":"的確冇講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以唔好再話佢地蠢/fake news on9冇人睇<br />\n真蠢只會做一次，做得多一定有佢既理由<br />\n<br />\n策略上，循例點都要餵返啲blue pill俾支持者食<br />\n因為佢地最怕既係啲人食red pill"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:14:28.000Z","msg":"而且韓國瑜依粒藍色藥除左希望支持者安於現狀之外，仲包埋幫高雄發大財、抗疫同團結社會嘅效用用<br />\n好難叫人唔食多幾粒姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港朋友係咪好葡萄呢？ 唔怕！<br />\n我地都有郭安法依粒多功能藥丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}